<li><strong>$include_base</strong> (<em>bool</em>) &#8211; Whether to include BASEPATH</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="field-even field"><th class="field-name">Returns:</th><td class="field-body"><p class="first">An array of package paths</p>
</td>
